entries.title: Blacksun Hero: Arlem Demonhunter!
entries.title_d: 'Arlem Demonhunter... a hero of the Blacksun! Rumored to take on a whole Car'das fleet single-handedly! When I've defeated the Black Sun hero, I should return to Aleas.'
